♪You said you would be with me♪

13
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:35,180
=Six Sisters=

14
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 33=

15
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,480
Hey, Xiaoling.

16
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:45,920
Don't touch anything.

17
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,560
The equipment is very expensive.

18
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,590
If you break it, in no way can we pay.

19
00:01:49,590 --> 00:01:50,840
Fine, fine.

20
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,510
This is the employee manual.

21
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:54,510
It offers the workflow and guidelines.

22
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:56,350
- Read it carefully.
- Ok.

23
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:58,430
Later, someone will guide you.

24
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,310
Alright.

25
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,480
Don't worry.

26
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,510
Sharp eyes are my best advantage.

27
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:03,510
Sharp eyes aren't enough.

28
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:05,230
You must be patient and careful.

29
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,150
Oh, the internship period is six months.

30
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:11,800
You must pass the qualification exam

31
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,040
before you're officially hired.

32
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:15,640
Then...

33
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:19,440
Is there a salary for the internship?

34
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:20,880
No, according to the rules.

35
00:02:21,150 --> 00:02:23,150
But Hongyu's brother
knows the boss very well.

36
00:02:23,150 --> 00:02:24,230
He got you a salary.

37
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,390
Enough for meals, anyway.

38
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:29,430
Jiaxi, you're such a good sister.

39
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:30,360
Of course.

40
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,230
Xiaoling,

41
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:33,750
your job

42
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,150
is almost settled down.

43
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:36,830
Move out of Mom's home, then.

44
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:38,560
Don't worry.

45
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,880
I've found somewhere to live.

46
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,200
- Where is it?
- It's not far.

47
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,120
Near Jiawen's home.

48
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,200
A small bungalow.

49
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:47,590
That's good.

50
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,430
Work hard.

51
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:49,710
- Ok.
- Let's move on.

52
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:50,550
Sure.

53
00:02:56,750 --> 00:02:57,950
Xiaoling.

54
00:02:58,870 --> 00:02:59,790
- We're here.
- Welcome,

55
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,120
sisters.

56
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:08,830
This room looks good. Is the rent high?

57
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,840
No. It's a cheap house.
I just pay a little

58
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,230
and I'll take care of the house.

59
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,040
Oh, there's another room.

60
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,360
It's enough for you alone.

61
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,840
Yeah. It looks very big.

62
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,710
Right.

63
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,560
It just doesn't have a toilet.

64
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,710
I need to go out.

65
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,720
Just like when we lived in the north.

66
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,620
Right.

67
00:03:28,320 --> 00:03:30,200
My life is getting even worse.

68
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,150
This one-family house is awesome.

69
00:03:32,150 --> 00:03:33,040
It's quiet.

70
00:03:33,150 --> 00:03:34,400
Well, you guys talk.

71
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,240
I go to the toilet.

72
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,800
Ok. Turn right and go down the street.

73
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,640
I know.

74
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,630
Sit, Jiali. Sit down.

75
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,280
I don't want to stain your bed.

76
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,360
Do you despise this house?

77
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,760
That's not true.

78
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,510
Be seated.

79
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,440
Look at me.

80
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:56,990
I've got a job.

81
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,110
I have somewhere to live, too.

82
00:03:59,750 --> 00:04:01,790
I can even profit
from the rent difference.

83
00:04:02,570 --> 00:04:05,510
Yes. Your life is back on track.

84
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:09,040
But Yangyang...

85
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:10,850
Can you think of a way for me?

86
00:04:12,350 --> 00:04:14,910
When I saw two rooms
and two beds here,

87
00:04:14,910 --> 00:04:16,940
I knew you wanted to get Yangyang here.

88
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,510
This place, you know,

89
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:21,600
is near his school.

90
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,910
It's convenient for him.

91
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:26,390
You're always careless.

92
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,190
Now, you can use your brain.

93
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,910
I can always use my brain.

94
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,510
Oh, poor mother.

95
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,030
Thanks.

96
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,150
Alright. Go check it.

97
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:52,760
Ok, Jiayi.

98
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,840
Please enter the password.

99
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:00,980
(Checking)

100
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:02,620
(Balance: 104,000 yuan
Available: 104,000 yuan)

101
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,350
The money is in.

102
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,630
Jiayi, good luck with your business.

103
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,760
From your lips to God's ears.

104
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,430
Now, we're even.

105
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:13,560
Yes, indeed.

106
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,150
Where will you move?

107
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,030
What? Will you offer a flat?

108
00:05:27,450 --> 00:05:29,150
I live and eat in the hotel.

109
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,310
I even plan
to spend my last years there.

110
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:32,800
I have no flats.

111
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,120
Here. Take a look.

112
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,510
Don't touch the card
after touching my feet.

113
00:05:42,510 --> 00:05:43,390
That's jinxed.

114
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:44,750
I love to see the number.

115
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,760
Let me see it. Hurry.

116
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,910
Come on. You'll see it like this.

117
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,190
When you have time these days,

118
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,480
tidy up our home.

119
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,950
Move big things to Xiaoling's house.

120
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,160
We'll take away the small ones.

121
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:00,200
Where are we moving, then?

122
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:04,000
Yan Hongyu, what's wrong with you?

123
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,160
To my mom's house.

124
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,710
Didn't we have a deal?

125
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,350
What if Jiali is upset?

126
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:11,760
Don't be scared.

127
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,440
Problems must be solved.

128
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:14,830
Sooner or later.

129
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,240
Jiali,

130
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:28,950
doing laundry, huh?

131
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:32,640
I have something to tell you.

132
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,800
You go inside.

133
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,240
I'll finish the laundry first.

134
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:37,390
It's ok. I can talk here.

135
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:41,750
Xiaoman's household registration
is transferred here.

136
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,920
She'll enroll soon.

137
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:44,880
In autumn, she'll go to primary school.

138
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,600
Her grandma said

139
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,910
she could live there.

140
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:50,430
But I think that's far and inconvenient.

141
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:52,440
I'll be worried
if her grandma looks after her.

142
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,200
So, maybe,

143
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:56,270
we have to move back here.

144
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,590
Ok.

145
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,440
Jiali, to be honest,

146
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:05,030
I don't just move back for Xiaoman.

147
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,560
I also want

148
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,640
to share your burden.

149
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:10,800
You took care of Grandma
in her last years.

150
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,880
You'll take care of Mom, too.

151
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,040
Sisters like us

152
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,560
all think you work too hard.

153
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,390
You've been taking care of this family.

154
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:18,740
You deserve some rest.

155
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:24,510
Besides, you should also

156
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:26,830
take care of Xiaonian's child.

157
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:28,830
You can't ignore your grandchild.

158
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,350
There's no hurry, Jiali.

159
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:39,640
We'll move before school begins.

160
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,070
Think about it.

161
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:46,080
Xiaonian lived here
when he went to school.

162
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,870
Now, Xiaoman will go to school.

163
00:07:48,770 --> 00:07:49,880
How time flies.

164
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:55,450
This house is quite prosperous.

165
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:06,240
Just now, Jiaxi came,

166
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,840
officially informing us

167
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:11,040
Xiaoman would go to school in autumn

168
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,170
and they would move back.

169
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:14,320
She wanted us to get out now.

170
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,710
Did she really say that?

171
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,620
You must be exaggerating.

172
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,880
That's what she actually means.

173
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,080
Xiaoman will go to school.

174
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,830
That's exactly why

175
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,890
her registration is back here.

176
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:28,030
I'm not surprised.

177
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,590
The two of us

178
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,320
will live somewhere else.

179
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:33,470
Don't fall out with them.

180
00:08:33,590 --> 00:08:34,600
When Xiaoling was back,

181
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:36,360
Jiaxi was really busy.

182
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:38,710
She offered a lot of ideas.

183
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,680
See? She moved Xiaoling out.

184
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,200
Now, she's kicking us out.

185
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,440
Don't say that.

186
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,110
Jiaxi's request is reasonable.

187
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:49,630
When she wants
to take care of Mom, let her be.

188
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,830
That's a good thing.

189
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,840
Mom must have pampered her.

190
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,750
Without permission,

191
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:54,630
she wouldn't dare.

192
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:57,150
Mom has a big problem with us.

193
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:59,830
So, we need an early plan.

194
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:01,870
What plan?

195
00:09:04,750 --> 00:09:05,800
Rent a flat.

196
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,440
How about

197
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,230
we buy a flat?

198
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:13,590
Shall we live with Xiaonian?

199
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,470
Don't make more trouble.

200
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:17,910
Distance makes heart grow fonder.

201
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:18,960
When they got married,

202
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:21,000
we didn't live with them.

203
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,550
Our son and his wife

204
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:23,680
will just be relatives

205
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,080
who we sometimes visit.

206
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:26,520
We will

207
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,710
buy a small flat.

208
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,920
We'll stay there until we die.

209
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,920
We won't move out of there.

210
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:35,920
That's good.

211
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,590
But do you have money?

212
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,710
We'll think of a way.

213
00:09:40,140 --> 00:09:41,150
What way?

214
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,230
Can you do magic?

215
00:09:44,550 --> 00:09:46,080
I'll get the money.

216
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:51,900
(Always be alert
Huainan Detention Center)

217
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:01,440
Dad, did we get the wrong news?

218
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,080
Wait patiently.

219
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,630
When you see your mom,

220
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:12,560
give her the bouquet spiritedly.

221
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:13,870
It's been over a year.

222
00:10:13,870 --> 00:10:15,350
Make her happy.

223
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:21,740
(Huainan Detention Center)

224
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,600
(Detention Area)

225
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:30,440
♪The sun rests on the sea♪

226
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:37,470
♪The sky steals the night and day♪

227
00:10:39,710 --> 00:10:45,070
♪The waves tug at my heartstrings♪

228
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:50,170
Mom!

229
00:10:54,250 --> 00:10:58,640
♪The wind is blowing on my face♪

230
00:11:00,810 --> 00:11:06,190
♪I'm stroking the fragile film♪

231
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:13,150
♪Memories spread under the streetlamps♪

232
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:14,630
You've lost weight.

233
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:17,960
♪The stars linger♪

234
00:11:18,310 --> 00:11:20,850
♪In the Milky Way♪

235
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:25,450
Go home.

236
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,660
We're going home.

237
00:11:33,390 --> 00:11:34,230
Zhicheng,

238
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:35,400
take your mom home.

239
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,440
Let's go.

240
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,960
♪You laughed♪

241
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:48,250
♪You said you would be with me♪

242
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:09,460
Mom, when you were away,

243
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:11,220
I studied very hard

244
00:12:11,220 --> 00:12:12,700
to give you a surprise.

245
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:14,620
Now, I've made progress.

246
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:17,020
I ranked third
from the bottom in my class.

247
00:12:17,020 --> 00:12:19,020
Now I rank 37th from the top.

248
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:21,820
What's the truth? Be honest.

249
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:24,980
Fifth from the bottom.

250
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:28,180
With persistent efforts,

251
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:30,300
he made progress, anyway.

252
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:31,620
A little bit.

253
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:33,340
Mom,

254
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:36,500
Dad especially made the dishes for you.

255
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:37,740
Very delicious.

256
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:39,580
Jiahuan,

257
00:12:40,170 --> 00:12:41,730
you must have had poor meals lately.

258
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:44,740
Try if they taste as good as before.

259
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:46,420
Dad, the wine.

260
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:48,060
Oh, yes.

261
00:12:48,820 --> 00:12:49,660
Here it is.

262
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:54,220
Come on, son.

263
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:56,300
Let's raise our glasses

264
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:58,620
to celebrate Mom's safe return.

265
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,260
- Jiahuan.
- Here.

266
00:13:51,780 --> 00:13:53,060
Drink the milk.

267
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:10,060
You're out here.
Don't think about it anymore.

268
00:14:13,330 --> 00:14:14,580
The manager is dead.

269
00:14:17,580 --> 00:14:18,660
It's all over.

270
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:19,820
Let it go.

271
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,000
But I'm innocent.

272
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,100
Of course, you are.

273
00:14:24,100 --> 00:14:25,940
I'm not innocent
because he killed himself.

274
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:26,980
I'm just innocent.

275
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:27,980
I'm not involved in this.

276
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:28,980
I didn't know what he did.

277
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:29,940
I really didn't know.

278
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:31,020
- I'm innocent.
- I know.

279
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:31,900
I know.

280
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:33,220
I know everything.

281
00:14:34,340 --> 00:14:35,220
I really do.

282
00:14:46,340 --> 00:14:48,060
It's not too late to leave me now.

283
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:51,820
Don't be ridiculous.

284
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:54,380
I have nothing now.

285
00:14:55,380 --> 00:14:56,540
And I'm nobody.

286
00:14:56,540 --> 00:14:57,420
It doesn't matter.

287
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:01,220
I can't get my old job back.

288
00:15:01,220 --> 00:15:02,740
I can't go back to work.

289
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:04,180
My previous efforts are wasted.

290
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:05,940
Everything's in vain. I can't go back.

291
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:06,780
I've lost everything.

292
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:08,380
- I'm not what I used to be.
- Jiahuan.

293
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:10,260
Jiahuan, I said it's ok.

294
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:14,620
I was laid off, too.

295
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:18,300
Jiayi and Ouyang rose again, right?

296
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:21,460
As long as we're alive,

297
00:15:22,070 --> 00:15:23,860
we can start all over again.

298
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:29,860
So, this is how it feels
to be abandoned by destiny.

299
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,780
My family is gone.

300
00:15:33,460 --> 00:15:34,340
My job is gone.

301
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:36,260
So is my pride.

302
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:37,460
I've lost everything.

303
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:38,740
You still have me.

304
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:42,340
And our son.

305
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,780
When our family sticks together,

306
00:15:45,460 --> 00:15:46,820
nothing will be a problem.

307
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:50,300
Jiahuan,

308
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,740
get some sleep now.

309
00:15:53,740 --> 00:15:54,620
In a couple of days,

310
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:56,980
we'll get remarried.

311
00:16:05,660 --> 00:16:07,580
Why don't you leave me?

312
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:16,500
I couldn't live

313
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:21,500
without you.

