324
00:17:19,050 --> 00:17:23,840
♪How can I tell you♪

325
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:29,390
♪Flowers bloom in distant corners♪

326
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:34,360
♪What can I offer you♪

327
00:17:35,290 --> 00:17:39,740
♪Mountains, rivers, and clouds♪

328
00:17:39,950 --> 00:17:44,880
♪What can I give back to you♪

329
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:50,340
♪My heart is restless♪

330
00:17:50,340 --> 00:17:53,350
♪What can I leave to you♪

331
00:17:53,420 --> 00:17:55,260
- Take it.
- Mom.

332
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,140
It's for you.

333
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,280
It's ok.

334
00:18:06,670 --> 00:18:07,860
Do you think

335
00:18:08,980 --> 00:18:10,100
I'm a loser?

336
00:18:10,100 --> 00:18:10,980
No.

337
00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:12,780
Since you were born,

338
00:18:13,980 --> 00:18:17,580
you've been my smartest daughter.

339
00:18:18,020 --> 00:18:22,300
You are the first
college student in this family.

340
00:18:22,620 --> 00:18:24,860
You're everyone's pride.

341
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:27,940
I didn't do anything wrong.

342
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:28,790
Mom, trust me.

343
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,020
I wouldn't do that.

344
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:31,260
I trust you.

345
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:34,860
Forget it.

346
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,820
What's gone is gone.

347
00:18:37,540 --> 00:18:38,860
Pretend you had a fall.

348
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:42,220
Now, you rise again. Ok?

349
00:18:42,620 --> 00:18:44,820
You'll live an ordinary life.

350
00:18:45,700 --> 00:18:47,700
Just be safe and happy.

351
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:48,740
Right?

352
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:50,820
You're quite lucky.

353
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:54,220
Look. Fang Tao loves you so much.

354
00:18:54,220 --> 00:18:56,020
All these years...

355
00:19:02,390 --> 00:19:03,230
Aunt Xiaoling.

356
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:04,460
Give me a shrimp.

357
00:19:04,460 --> 00:19:05,300
Shrimp, huh?

358
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:06,140
Don't eat too much.

359
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:07,020
Have a shrimp.

360
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:08,940
Give more to Jiahuan.

361
00:19:08,940 --> 00:19:09,940
- Be careful.
- Thanks.

362
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:11,380
Thanks.

363
00:19:11,500 --> 00:19:12,340
Let's drink.

364
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:13,620
- Try the beans.
- Ok.

365
00:19:13,780 --> 00:19:15,060
- Eat more.
- Ok.

366
00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,460
Jiahuan is free.

367
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:17,980
Xiaoling is back, too.

368
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:20,580
Now, we have a family reunion.

369
00:19:21,100 --> 00:19:22,820
Hope we'll be better.

370
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:23,980
To better days.

371
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:25,020
- Better days.
- Jiahuan.

372
00:19:25,220 --> 00:19:26,340
- Welcome back.
- Cheers.

373
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:27,180
Cheers.

374
00:19:28,020 --> 00:19:29,300
Congratulations, Jiahuan. Cheers.

375
00:19:33,260 --> 00:19:35,620
Jiahuan, how did it feel
when you were in there?

376
00:19:40,540 --> 00:19:42,020
Xiaoling, have some pork.

377
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:43,420
It's really tasty.

378
00:19:43,420 --> 00:19:44,260
Ok.

379
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:47,260
Xiaoling, you can get in there

380
00:19:47,620 --> 00:19:48,500
and experience that.

381
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:49,580
I don't dare.

382
00:19:51,060 --> 00:19:52,140
- Jiahuan.
- Eat.

383
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:56,420
Later, get remarried to Fang Tao.

384
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:00,220
What do you mean?

385
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,860
Why will you get remarried?

386
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:05,220
Did you divorce?

387
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:09,000
I missed a lot of exciting stories.

388
00:20:09,180 --> 00:20:10,720
Xiaoling, have some shrimp.

389
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:12,730
Here.

390
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,660
We know you have a tongue.

391
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:22,380
How's your job?

392
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:25,340
I quit.

393
00:20:25,780 --> 00:20:27,180
- Have some shrimp.
- No worries.

394
00:20:27,540 --> 00:20:29,180
Adjust your mood first.

395
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,860
Then, we'll see.

396
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:33,700
Get her a shrimp.

397
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:34,940
- Where's Guangming?
- She doesn't want it.

398
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:37,140
- Guangming.
- He...

399
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:39,700
He'll have the exam.

400
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:40,940
So, I didn't invite him.

401
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:41,860
He'll come next time.

402
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:43,780
That's right.

403
00:20:44,060 --> 00:20:46,660
I guess only Guangming
will be successful.

404
00:20:47,380 --> 00:20:48,220
That depends.

405
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:50,580
All roads lead to Rome.

406
00:20:51,020 --> 00:20:52,100
Which school is Feng in?

407
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,180
I'm in a vocational college.

408
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:54,620
That's right.

409
00:20:55,780 --> 00:20:56,620
That's good.

410
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:57,780
We're satisfied.

411
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,260
Let me say something.

412
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:05,140
Jianguo and I

413
00:21:05,700 --> 00:21:07,220
will move out, too.

414
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:08,900
Why?

415
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:10,260
Mom,

416
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,580
what's going on?

417
00:21:13,900 --> 00:21:16,340
Xiaoman is going to primary school.

418
00:21:16,340 --> 00:21:18,100
Jiaxi will move back in.

419
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:23,420
Yeah. Xiaoman's grandma is competitive.

420
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:25,220
Xiaoman has to go to HNU Primary School.

421
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:27,580
It makes sense.

422
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:28,500
A child

423
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:30,380
should have a head start.

424
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:32,380
When Mom is still strong enough,

425
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:34,100
she can help take care of Xiaoman.

426
00:21:35,130 --> 00:21:36,260
She doesn't need to.

427
00:21:37,540 --> 00:21:39,100
I'll take care of Xiaoman myself.

428
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:41,220
I'm not moving back to bother Mom.

429
00:21:41,580 --> 00:21:44,060
Besides, I can also take care of Mom.

430
00:21:44,820 --> 00:21:45,940
Hongyu said

431
00:21:45,940 --> 00:21:47,700
we had a responsibility
to take care of Mom.

432
00:21:48,020 --> 00:21:49,020
That's right.

433
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:51,620
Mom, where will you and Dad live?

434
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:53,620
How about you live with us?

435
00:21:55,780 --> 00:21:58,500
Mom, our home is the stronghold for you.

436
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,100
Welcome back anytime.

437
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:10,420
Come on.

438
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,780
Have another drink. Cheers.

439
00:22:12,580 --> 00:22:13,660
- Cheers.
- You guys drink.

440
00:22:13,660 --> 00:22:15,020
Let's drink. Come on, Tao.

441
00:22:15,020 --> 00:22:15,860
Cheers.

442
00:22:16,380 --> 00:22:18,980
Who is she to make you move out?

443
00:22:19,580 --> 00:22:21,300
She knows you have nowhere to live now.

444
00:22:21,300 --> 00:22:22,860
She must be on purpose.

445
00:22:26,860 --> 00:22:27,700
I understand.

446
00:22:28,300 --> 00:22:30,020
Nonsense.

447
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:32,460
Xiaoman was registered here
a long time ago.

448
00:22:32,820 --> 00:22:35,020
It can't be a sudden plan.

449
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:36,740
Just a matter of time.

450
00:22:36,740 --> 00:22:38,820
Can't you restrain her as you did

451
00:22:38,820 --> 00:22:39,660
in our childhood?

452
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,740
Why aren't you as tough as before?

453
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,860
You've grown up.

454
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,580
You're even mothers.

455
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,640
I can't restrain you
like I did in childhood?

456
00:22:49,170 --> 00:22:52,140
The problem is she can easily move in

457
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:53,700
but won't easily move out.

458
00:22:54,020 --> 00:22:55,820
I don't expect her to move out.

459
00:22:55,940 --> 00:22:58,180
I just want her
to take good care of Mom.

460
00:22:58,740 --> 00:23:00,900
Is she actually a caring woman?

461
00:23:08,380 --> 00:23:11,220
Mom brought Jiaxi up. They're close.

462
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:13,980
If she takes care of Mom
when Mom's old,

463
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,180
that's ok.

464
00:23:16,340 --> 00:23:18,020
We should give Mom some money

465
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:19,900
in case people gossip.

466
00:23:24,810 --> 00:23:28,160
But you need somewhere to live.

467
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:31,380
My husband wants

468
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:32,780
to buy a small flat.

469
00:23:33,780 --> 00:23:34,820
A pre-owned one.

470
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:38,620
We'll see. We can rent one first.

471
00:23:55,540 --> 00:23:56,420
It's ok.

472
00:23:57,300 --> 00:23:58,420
Jiali didn't say anything.

473
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,100
What would she say?

474
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:00,940
What could she say?

475
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,780
Her silence was worse than complaint!

476
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,980
She said she'd move out
in front of the whole family.

477
00:24:04,980 --> 00:24:07,180
Why? So, everybody has to take a side.

478
00:24:07,180 --> 00:24:08,060
Listen, Yan Hongyu.

479
00:24:08,060 --> 00:24:09,940
Let's bet. Believe it or not,
this isn't over.

480
00:24:09,940 --> 00:24:11,540
Maybe we can't move back there.

481
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,640
It won't happen.

482
00:24:12,640 --> 00:24:13,680
It won't?

483
00:24:14,570 --> 00:24:15,850
She won't make a scene.

484
00:24:15,850 --> 00:24:17,290
But she'll make someone else do that.

485
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:19,890
Didn't you see?
Jiawen pulled a long face immediately.

486
00:24:19,890 --> 00:24:21,290
Jiayi looked upset, too.

487
00:24:21,290 --> 00:24:22,210
Jiahuan looked alright.

488
00:24:22,210 --> 00:24:24,010
Maybe she is still confused out of jail.

489
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:25,890
Think about Xiaoling.
She wants something, too.

490
00:24:26,010 --> 00:24:27,690
You think others don't want benefits?

491
00:24:27,690 --> 00:24:30,170
Maybe they think we'll move back there

492
00:24:30,170 --> 00:24:31,490
for Mom's house

493
00:24:31,490 --> 00:24:32,770
and her pension.

494
00:24:33,370 --> 00:24:35,530
We really want her house, don't we?

495
00:24:35,540 --> 00:24:36,450
No!

496
00:24:36,850 --> 00:24:38,350
I do this for Xiaoman's education.

497
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,470
Fine.

498
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:40,530
Let's not talk about this.

499
00:24:41,050 --> 00:24:42,810
Since Jiali brought it up,

500
00:24:42,810 --> 00:24:44,250
it's now on the calendar.

501
00:24:45,090 --> 00:24:47,650
Jiali is in the wrong industry.

502
00:24:47,810 --> 00:24:49,050
She should have been an actress.

503
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:50,490
Maybe she'd be the Best Actress.

504
00:24:50,610 --> 00:24:51,690
Think about her big eyes.

505
00:24:51,690 --> 00:24:53,050
When she stares with tears,

506
00:24:53,050 --> 00:24:54,370
everybody will pity her.

507
00:24:55,850 --> 00:24:56,970
But it makes sense.

508
00:24:57,570 --> 00:24:58,650
I'm sure she thinks

509
00:24:58,650 --> 00:25:00,610
she's sacrificed a lot for this family.

510
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,040
But she didn't expect

511
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:04,000
she and Mom
couldn't get along very well.

512
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,040
Mom didn't ask her to stay.

513
00:25:05,040 --> 00:25:06,160
Alright.

514
00:25:07,120 --> 00:25:08,120
Say no more.

515
00:25:08,320 --> 00:25:10,280
Stop thinking. Don't go crazy.

516
00:25:10,280 --> 00:25:11,760
Or you'll be too angry to sleep.

517
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:19,480
Stop thinking. Come on.

518
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:29,720
(Tianjia'an Civil Affairs Bureau
July 19, 2002)

519
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:30,680
Come on. Smile.

520
00:25:31,780 --> 00:25:32,760
Ma'am, smile.

521
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:34,720
Ok.

522
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:47,740
(Marriage Registration)

523
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:50,220
I'm qualified to cook for you again.

524
00:25:52,320 --> 00:25:55,500
I can only offer steamed buns and rice.

525
00:25:55,820 --> 00:25:57,100
You don't want steak?

526
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:59,620
Then, I want sweet bean sauce on it.

527
00:26:04,140 --> 00:26:10,300
(Fang Tao)

528
00:26:10,300 --> 00:26:12,100
(Admission Ticket)

529
00:26:15,580 --> 00:26:16,580
My heart is racing.

530
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:18,260
Come on. My heart races, too.

531
00:26:19,100 --> 00:26:23,900
You're admitted
to Jiangnan Forestry University.

532
00:26:33,460 --> 00:26:35,380
Jiangnan Forestry University?

533
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:38,250
Did he apply for that?

534
00:26:38,260 --> 00:26:39,100
Yes.

535
00:26:39,930 --> 00:26:40,780
Ok.

536
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:43,700
Where is this university?

537
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:46,700
At the foot of the Purple Mountain
in suburban Nanjing.

538
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:48,260
So,

539
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:50,820
it's not far from Sun Yat-sen Mausoleum.

540
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,340
It's a good place.

541
00:26:54,980 --> 00:26:57,220
Yes. Good, indeed.

542
00:26:57,220 --> 00:26:58,740
The air must be good.

543
00:27:02,180 --> 00:27:04,500
Well done, son.

544
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:06,320
You're going to college.

545
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,660
Very good.

546
00:27:19,140 --> 00:27:20,020
Jiaxi,

547
00:27:20,140 --> 00:27:21,780
you should move out soon.

548
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,980
I'm waiting to renovate this house.

549
00:27:24,340 --> 00:27:26,060
When it's cold,
the smell won't dissipate.

550
00:27:26,300 --> 00:27:27,620
I'm more anxious than you.

551
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:30,300
Fine. Glad you know what to do.

552
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:31,460
I should go.

553
00:27:33,340 --> 00:27:34,660
Jiayi, have an ice pop.

554
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:35,980
No.

555
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:37,940
I'm too old to eat icy food.

556
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:41,380
Stop cooling yourself.
Here. Have an ice pop.

557
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:46,500
Yan Hongyu, are you insane?

558
00:27:46,500 --> 00:27:47,980
Do you think an ice pop will work?

559
00:27:48,500 --> 00:27:49,340
I won't eat it.

560
00:27:53,420 --> 00:27:54,900
It's so hot.

561
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:57,220
The fan doesn't even work.

562
00:27:57,380 --> 00:27:58,860
I need the air-conditioner.

563
00:27:59,020 --> 00:28:00,380
Don't be ridiculous.

564
00:28:00,380 --> 00:28:01,620
We're moving away soon.

565
00:28:03,020 --> 00:28:03,900
Soon?

566
00:28:06,230 --> 00:28:07,220
You know what?

